WEBVTT

00:02.167 --> 00:03.400
Man: HOLY [BLEEP].

00:03.433 --> 00:06.700
Narrator: PREVIOUSLY,
ON "DEADLIEST CATCH"...

00:06.733 --> 00:09.500
Keith: THE BERING SEA
HAS BECOME STORM ALLEY --

00:09.533 --> 00:12.067
ONE STORM AFTER ANOTHER
AFTER ANOTHER.

00:12.100 --> 00:14.400
-WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!
-THERE IT GOES!

00:14.433 --> 00:16.833
Jake: GET OFF MY DECK, DEAN.

00:16.867 --> 00:18.400
YOU'RE FIRED!

00:18.433 --> 00:21.033
WHOA! WHOA! WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!
WHOA! WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!

00:21.067 --> 00:24.200
I DON'T UNDERSTAND WHY IT HURTS
SO MUCH RIGHT HERE.

00:24.233 --> 00:26.100
UH, GOING INTO OPILIOS NOW,

00:26.133 --> 00:30.500
I WOULD FEEL PRETTY FOOLISH
TO GO UP THERE, PUSH MY LUCK.

00:33.267 --> 00:35.600
I JUST TOOK A NITRO PILL
WHILE I WAS TALKING TO MY WIFE.

00:35.633 --> 00:36.800
SHE'S LIKE, "TAKE ONE,"

00:36.833 --> 00:41.733
BECAUSE I WAS FEELING PAIN
UNDER HERE, HERE.

00:41.767 --> 00:43.367
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME.

